    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the style and culture of the Wolastoqiyik, also known as Maliseet or Malecite, a First Nations indigenous people belonging to the Wabanaki Confederacy, together with the Passamaquoddy, Penobscot, Mi'kmaq, and Abenaki Indians. The Wolastoqiyik mainly live in Canada, especially New Brunswick, with one group across the border in nearby Maine.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000047301/Native Languages of America (n.d.)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refierese a la cultura del Maliseet, una tribu americana nativa que pertenece a la confederación de los indios americanos del este, conocidos como la alianza de Wabanaki, junto con los Passamaquoddy, Penobscot, Micmac, y los indios de Abnaki. El Maliseet principalmente vivo en Canadá, especialmente en New Brunswick, grupo cercano a la frontera en Maine.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Verwijst naar de cultuur van de Maliseet, een inheemse Amerikaanse stam die behoort tot de losse confederatie van oostelijk Amerikaanse indianen die bekend staan als de Wabanaki-alliantie, samen met de Passamaquoddy-, Penobscot-, Micmac- en Abnaki-indianen. De Maliseet wonen hoofdzakelijk in Canada, vooral in New Brunswick, terwijl één groep over de grens woont, in het nabijgelegen Maine.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052384/Billard, De indianen (1978)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>指麥勒席族之文化，該族群隸屬於東美洲印第安人的鬆散邦聯，即為一般所知的瓦班納基聯盟（Wabanaki Alliance），該聯盟由麥勒席族與帕薩馬科迪族（Passamaquoddy）、皮納布斯高族（Penobscot）、密克馬克族（Micmac）及艾布納基族（Abnaki）組成。麥勒席人主要居住於加拿大地區，特別是在新伯倫瑞克省，該族的其中一支則越過了美加邊界，分佈於鄰近的緬因州地區。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
